data.description: COMING, SPRING 2022! Dreaming of a BRAND-NEW home with a view of the Sangres and a short drive to restaurants and shopping? This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is not only AFFORDABLE, but the construction is impeccable. The finishes in the home are exquisite, including the lavish kitchen with stainless steel appliances, vaulted ceilings and a wood burning stove for those snowy winter nights. Not to mention the laundry suite and 2 walk-in closets. Walk out onto your patio to enjoy the mountain views. The home is EFFICIENT, inviting and a great place to host. Whether this is your full-time home or vacation RETREAT, you can't go wrong with a 1-year WARRANTY from the local builders. With room in the back to store your boat or camper, the opportunities here are endless!
